---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout>
  <main>
    <h1 id="next-generation-cartographers">
      <a href="../">
        <img
          src="/assets/ngc-marks/ngc-rgb-logotype-4c.svg"
          class="logo"
          alt="Next Generation Cartographers"
        />
      </a>
      <span style="display: none">Next Generation Cartographers</span>
      <span>Branding manual</span>
    </h1>

    <p>
      We try to keep the branding for
      <span class="inline-logo">NGC</span> light to make it easy to use. If you have
      questions, comments or ideas on how we can improve the branding we are happy
      to hear them. Please reach out to us via
      <a href="https://discord.gg/3vbDshHjf3">discord</a>.
    </p>

    <h2>Idea / Concept</h2>
    <svg width="40" height="40">
      <path d="M 5 35 A 20 20 0 1 1 35 35 Z"></path>
      <line
        x1="0"
        x2="40"
        transform="translate(0, 39)"
        stroke-width="4"
        stroke="black"></line>
    </svg>
    <p>
      The sunrise symbolizes an optimistic future â€“ each new day entails hope
      and opportunities . As <span class="inline-logo">NGC</span> we want to promote
      this perspective on the future on the basis of our cores values: inclusiveness,
      diversity, and openness.
      <span class="inline-logo">NGC</span>
      is a network and a safe space based on mutual trust and respect.
    </p>
    <p>
      The branding includes marks, fonts and colors for now and might be adapted
      and extended as the community and its work change.
    </p>

    <h2 id="resources">Download resources</h2>
    <ul class="link-list">
      <li class="link-card">
        <a
          href="https://github.com/next-generation-cartographers/next-generation-cartographers.github.io/tree/main/ngc-marks"
        >
          <h2>
            Marks
            <span style="font-family: var(--font-family-body)">&rarr;</span>
          </h2>
          <p>Download the marks in different variants and file formats.</p>
        </a>
      </li>
      <li class="link-card">
        <a href="https://github.com/floriankarsten/space-grotesk/releases">
          <h2>
            Font: Space Grotesk
            <span style="font-family: var(--font-family-body)">&rarr;</span>
          </h2>
          <p>Download the headline font <em>Space Grotesk</em>.</p>
        </a>
      </li>
      <li class="link-card">
        <a href="https://github.com/adobe-fonts/source-sans/releases/">
          <h2>
            Font: Source Sans
            <span style="font-family: var(--font-family-body)">&rarr;</span>
          </h2>
          <p>Download the body copy font <em>Source Sans</em>.</p>
        </a>
      </li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Marks</h2>
    <p>
      All marks can be downloaded via github (see
      <a href="#resources">resources</a>). There are two types of marks: the
      logomark and the logotype. Both types exist in two color variants: the
      primary color variant and a light and a dark monochrome variant.
    </p>
    <h3>Logotype</h3>
    <div class="marks-grid">
      <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column">
        <img class="mark" src="/assets/ngc-marks/ngc-rgb-logotype-4c.svg" />
      </div>
    </div>
    <p>
      The Logotype should be used whenever possible. For applications where the
      subline of the logotype is no longer readable the logomark is preferred.
    </p>
    <h3>Logomark</h3>
    <div class="marks-grid">
      <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column">
        <img
          class="mark small"
          src="/assets/ngc-marks/ngc-rgb-logomark-4c.svg"
        />
      </div>
    </div>

    <h3>Monochrome variants</h3>
    <p>
      Two monochrome version of the marks exist: the dark variant for light
      backgrounds, the light variant for dark backgrounds.
    </p>
    <div class="marks-grid">
      <div>
        <h4>Dark monochrome</h4>
        <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1em">
          <img
            class="mark"
            src="/assets/ngc-marks/ngc-rgb-logotype-black.svg"
          />
          <img
            class="mark small"
            src="/assets/ngc-marks/ngc-rgb-logomark-black.svg"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h4>Light monochrome</h4>
        <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1em">
          <img
            class="mark"
            src="/assets/ngc-marks/ngc-rgb-logotype-white.svg"
          />
          <img
            class="mark small"
            src="/assets/ngc-marks/ngc-rgb-logomark-white.svg"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2>Typography</h2>
    <p>
      The headline font is <em>Space Grotesk</em> and the body copy font is
      <em>Source Sans</em>. Both fonts can be downloaded (see
      <a href="#resources">resources</a>).
    </p>
    <h3>Headline font</h3>
    <p
      style="
          margin: 1em 0 0;
          font-family: var(--font-family-headline);
          font-size: 36px;
          line-height: 1.25;
        "
    >
      The quick brown fox jumps over the lazy dog.
    </p>
    <p class="muted">Space Grotesk, Bold, 36px</p>
    <h3>Bodycopy font</h3>
    <p
      style="
          margin: 1em 0 0;
          font-family: var(--font-family-body);
          font-size: 36px;
          line-height: 1.25;
        "
    >
      The quick brown fox jumps over the lazy dog.
    </p>
    <p class="muted">Source Sans, Regular, 36px</p>
  </main>
</Layout>
